Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君今天輪到你值日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.42,0:01:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我把這份複印件交給今天感冒在家休息的古手川同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她家的地址也在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見啊  古手川居然會請假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來燒已經退得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點好的話  學習也要落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把藥和飯拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥今天怎麼沒去大學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  今天不去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可愛的妹妹正痛苦著呢  身為哥哥怎麼能去學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是逃課的理由哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.14,0:02:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦啊  吃完了就把盤子放在走廊上吧  我會收拾的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽出去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加鄰里聚會去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為能叫媽媽幫我擦擦身子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是別人托我來送東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但去女孩子的家還真是讓人緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  我是來把今天的複印件交給古手川唯同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  反正都來了就進來直接給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  這樣的話唯也會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  古手川…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…你哥…你哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知廉恥！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼結城君會到這裡來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你哥哥讓我進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣進女孩子房間前連門也不敲一下太不懂規矩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  那麼找我有什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班委拜託我把這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那現在身體怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒也退了  我想明天應該能去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  這太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:05:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是別人拜託他來的  但結城君居然會到我家裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在女孩子的房間裡兩人獨處還真是讓人覺得莫名的緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說些…不說些什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  感覺好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有放什麼怪東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古手川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好認真的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道很喜歡貓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  有什麼不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒不是  只是感到很意外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  古手川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把咖啡拿來…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你誤會個什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇…嚇了我一跳  沒想到唯那傢伙居然進展到這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算…算了  反正是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不太好意思待太久  會影響你休息的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒這事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒也已經退了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  又有客人來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶著大家都來探望你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  梨斗也來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  看上去氣色不錯啊  古手川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  鯛魚燒  是慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺這裡有好多貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  難道你很喜歡貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從御門老師那裡拿了很多藥過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}請
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的拿來了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我把唯同學感冒的事告訴御門老師後她就讓我多拿些過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜看這個看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我們兩個人獨處一會兒的話會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不知廉恥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  菈菈  要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的眼鏡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗我進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒整理出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過今天要回收可燃垃圾的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把可燃垃圾先整理出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這身打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是和平時一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平時一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要值日  先去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說現在是夏天  難道是正值青春期的原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間也來不及了  總之只能這樣戴著去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果菈菈已經到學校的話  也許能幫我把眼鏡拿下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也要做好最壞的打算  就這樣戴著這眼鏡過一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有摸到衣服  難道是因為這副眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是結城嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼戴了副眼鏡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:09:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西連寺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒和菈菈同學一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒看  我什麼都沒看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天做了春菜的春夢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈那傢伙  為什麼要發明出這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且到現在還沒來學校  這讓我怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦不  只是早上有點頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事  那個你剛剛要說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我從今天開始就是這班上的學生了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和結城君走的更近些就去拜託校長了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就唱了首即將發售的新曲  校長就同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這學校還真是隨意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後就能一直在一起了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有時候因為偶像工作要請假
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來怎麼戴了一副眼鏡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是菈菈的眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菈菈給你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為梨斗君不適合這副眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  太糟糕了  這次都能看到裸體了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  扎斯汀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的愛  就如同一對野兔  追隨對方到海角天涯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙…  沙姬小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這如同小鳥對翱翔藍天的渴望  究竟該怎麼做才…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你點教訓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟跑去哪裡了  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那邊找找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊  這樣下去根本沒辦法好好上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這是用來維護我發明品的  透透凝視君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會戴著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維護用的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對的  為了看機器內部構造而製造的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:12:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總  總之…  這東西怎麼取下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這稍微有些技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了  這樣下去肯定會遇到更大的麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君  這是我選的眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別戴那個土氣的了  換我的戴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露恩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快戴上這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把前面遮起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快取下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  別躲來躲去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把前面遮起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  雷恩  好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  發生了更糟糕的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦  猿山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近總是無精打彩的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  我好像犯了一見鍾情的病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一見鍾情？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  無論如何也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著男孩子的衣服  有男子氣概  沒戴胸罩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經在商店街有過一面之緣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣  我想辦法幫你約她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什麼啊  菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友在煩惱中不是嗎  當然要助他一臂之力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不也是梨斗一直以來的好友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:15:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說  但他所說的人是變成女孩子後的我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不正好  還省了去找的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經在等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要這樣做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦  因為對猿山說「已經找到了」啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用新製造的「滾滾男女君」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈還真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.71,0:15:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要脫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為馬上就要去約會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會…  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也  脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:15:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好準備內褲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被強行穿上這身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…是猿山健一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我…  啊  不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不能說結城這名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕崎梨子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨子  這名字真好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來真巧  梨子還是梨斗的遠親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  怪不得馬上就找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走啦  接下來就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們也走吧  梨子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  猿山君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這電影好像挺不錯哦  我來請客  一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:17:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看電影的話只要坐著不動就可以了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戀愛電影啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼和猿山一起看這種電影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很難為情  但我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是如此  如此地愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是如此  如此的…  愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是猿山同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩是你朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  她好像是梨斗的親戚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們千萬別做什麼不知羞恥的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是電影？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子不餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺有些累了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還帶了導遊書啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近好像是漢堡包最便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯛魚燒給你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  小闇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真讓人大吃一驚  竟然會在這裡遇到小闇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天一大早就去城裡的圖書館了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  要去唱下卡拉OK嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露恩小姐的新曲好像能唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露恩？  啊  那個梅莫魯西星人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為偶像後  一下就變得好有名氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著這麼客氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又變成女孩和猿山在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有優惠券不用擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是這方面的愛好覺醒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美柑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好累
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  感覺身體癢癢的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  第一次見面的時候真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒能克制住自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我…  我從那個時候開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那個時候開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  煙霧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就對你  對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一見鍾情！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然就變回原形了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉  滾滾男女君的有效時間好像過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊  有時間限時的話  一開始就該…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼穿著裙子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…  這是…  這是…  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}我  什麼也沒看見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤會了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  總是我  遇到這種倒楣事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這算是被甩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  怎麼能這樣就放棄了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後肯定還會見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候一定會讓你成為我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家務也是正規的勞動對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按每小時800日元  一天8個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.03,0:23:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一月30天  12個月的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.12,0:23:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然得要求增加零用錢才行！
